{"tid":2113422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴西200萬宗 印度100萬宗 美單日7萬宗  三國疫情再破頂","createTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T06:36:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"15077505d913b1d81d06aede3149b39a1eb03fbb","tid":2113422,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:10:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200718/UEHQLQVJIODGUVMSIUK55UJM4Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200718%2FUEHQLQVJIODGUVMSIUK55UJM4Q%2F&d=G%2B3HFD3c3HuaSfC8k9KTiazbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=0db1defd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200718%2FUEHQLQVJIODGUVMSIUK55UJM4Q%2F&h=88b9a3cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/20200718/UEHQLQVJIODGUVMSIUK55UJM4Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n巴西200萬宗 印度100萬宗 美單日7萬宗 <br />\n三國疫情再破頂<br />\n<br />\n【全球疫災】<br />\n<br />\n現時全球武漢肺炎疫情最嚴重三國，分別再破紀錄或突破關口，美國單日確診數字首次衝破7萬，巴西和印度累積確診數字，也分別突破200萬和100萬大關，反映出新熱點不斷出現下，全球疫情持續惡化，其中南亞快速成為疫情新震央。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/clbYomdSAnPiCxaHg_zo3RxWJC0=/964x581/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2DVN22YJFMLY5TDRYGID4QMNUU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FclbYomdSAnPiCxaHg_zo3RxWJC0%3D%2F964x581%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2DVN22YJFMLY5TDRYGID4QMNUU.gif&h=399ab2ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖保羅工人忙於挖掘墓地埋葬武肺死者。 路透社<br />\n<br />\n印度衞生部昨確認全國有逾100萬宗確診，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n印度的資訊科技中心班。。。。。。。。。實際感染數字可能達官方統計的20至30倍，未來數月將持續增加，現時最大挑戰是合理分配病床，盡量減少死亡數字。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qrnXMvVGKktSLPL4OGqrmyABB-4=/964x581/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6XGDEC4BNU4JDEKHZAXBI3F2AU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqrnXMvVGKktSLPL4OGqrmyABB-4%3D%2F964x581%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6XGDEC4BNU4JDEKHZAXBI3F2AU.gif&h=d6a23dd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新德里武肺檢測營有醫護昏倒，同袍趕忙協助。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n南亞成疫情新震央<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：東京疫情加劇 振興方案無份<br />\n<br />\n紅十字會與紅新月會國際聯合會前天表示，印度和分別有約26萬和20萬宗確診的巴基斯坦和孟加拉，正快速成為武肺疫情新震央，「當全球注意力集中在美國和南美持續的危機，人類悲劇正同時在佔全球四分一人口的南亞急速出現」。<br />\n<br />\n巴西衞生部前晚亦確認，。。。。。。。。。。。。令該國確診數字在27日內由100萬倍增，快於美國用了43日。<br />\n<br />\n里約熱內盧和亞馬遜州。。。。。。。。。。。死亡數字推算，巴西實際染疫人數或已達1,000萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n墨爾本封城仍劇增<br />\n<br />\n當地專家批評，巴西抗疫最大問題是各自為政，在測試和其他方面欠缺統籌，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n據路透社統計，美國前天新增破紀錄的77,217宗確診，累積近360萬宗確診和至少13.8萬死，德州、佛州和南卡羅來納州等近期疫情爆發熱點，單日死亡數字都創新高，德州和亞里桑那州多地更停屍間爆滿，需要額外冷藏櫃或冷藏貨櫃車穿暫時存放遺體。<br />\n<br />\n而澳洲第二大城市墨爾本在疫情重現後，雖已實行封鎖措施一周，但所屬維多利亞省昨天仍錄得428宗確診再破頂，比起3月底後任何一日的全國單日確診數字還要多。<br />\n<br />\n法新社/美聯社/路透社"},{"pid":"cf2d5d0f1bff66c6fd548ac79269cb78a8fe45ef","tid":2113422,"uid":72228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"好快美國帶頭打柒支那<br />\n呢d數支那好難找到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea113d488d908dab34c4c8a3f3ddf88f0148430","tid":2113422,"uid":261330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:30:59.000Z","msg":"香港日日50<br />\n信政府唔怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b29fd6e506682b3d99c7db35fef9fe757f591de","tid":2113422,"uid":191926,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T06:36:29.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對香港係好事<br />\n<br />\n親中勢力遭滅頂之災<br />\n<br />\n好像印度咁強硬  其中一個原因就係武肺"}]}